{"entity":{"id":"recUeIs4gxfoDB8La","type":"chapter","slug":"recUeIs4gxfoDB8La","label":"2Cor.2","rawId":"recUeIs4gxfoDB8La","book":{"id":"rec0CTDRtMnNCmQr9","type":"book","slug":"2cor","label":"2 Corinthians","subtitle":"Pauline Epistles","count":257,"description":"13 chapters, 122 people, 12 places"}},"stats":{"verses":17,"people":4,"places":2,"events":0},"nodes":[{"id":"recUeIs4gxfoDB8La","type":"chapter","group":"focus","label":"2Cor.2","slug":"2cor_2","score":17},{"id":"rec0CTDRtMnNCmQr9","type":"book","group":"book","label":"2 Corinthians","slug":"2cor","score":257},{"id":"recgkFqZovgbr3pAi","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Jesus Christ","slug":"jesus_905","score":5},{"id":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"God","slug":"god_1324","score":4},{"id":"recLFwe2uKBqJwmWn","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Satan","slug":"satan_2476","score":1},{"id":"rectkXUkoQk15fBk0","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Titus","slug":"titus_2869","score":1},{"id":"recOEIhMwampGbSqk","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Troas","slug":"troas_1182","score":1},{"id":"recly2TmP9CBHh8OQ","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Macedonia","slug":"macedonia_747","score":1}],"links":[{"source":"recUeIs4gxfoDB8La","target":"rec0CTDRtMnNCmQr9","label":"part of"},{"source":"recUeIs4gxfoDB8La","target":"recgkFqZovgbr3pAi","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recUeIs4gxfoDB8La","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recUeIs4gxfoDB8La","target":"recLFwe2uKBqJwmWn","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recUeIs4gxfoDB8La","target":"rectkXUkoQk15fBk0","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recUeIs4gxfoDB8La","target":"recOEIhMwampGbSqk","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recUeIs4gxfoDB8La","target":"recly2TmP9CBHh8OQ","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec0Psxj3iGo5cxkq","ref":"2Cor.2.1","text":"But I determined this with myself, that I would not come again to you in heaviness.","year":60},{"id":"recd032NHkMg4EKE3","ref":"2Cor.2.2","text":"For if I make you sorry, who is he then that maketh me glad, but the same which is made sorry by me?","year":60},{"id":"recHDdNxWRkSFuh55","ref":"2Cor.2.3","text":"And I wrote this same unto you, lest, when I came, I should have sorrow from them of whom I ought to rejoice; having confidence in you all, that my joy is the joy of you all.","year":60},{"id":"recAbGE0YIX9mudob","ref":"2Cor.2.4","text":"For out of much affliction and anguish of heart I wrote unto you with many tears; not that ye should be grieved, but that ye might know the love which I have more abundantly unto you.","year":60},{"id":"recSBxIvDVYglnQBc","ref":"2Cor.2.5","text":"But if any have caused grief, he hath not grieved me, but in part: that I may not overcharge you all.","year":60},{"id":"recHVpuw3f9B1hXwi","ref":"2Cor.2.6","text":"Sufficient to such a man is this punishment, which was inflicted of many.","year":60},{"id":"recGsFQpbJGSQJfsP","ref":"2Cor.2.7","text":"So that contrariwise ye ought rather to forgive him, and comfort him, lest perhaps such a one should be swallowed up with overmuch sorrow.","year":60},{"id":"recNaMGlUWahveqbe","ref":"2Cor.2.8","text":"Wherefore I beseech you that ye would confirm your love toward him.","year":60}]}
